The paper deals with algorithms for solving quadratic systems of equations, specifically the phase retrieval problem. This problem is related to signal processing and imaging, which suggests that the paper could belong to the cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.CV (Computer Vision) categories. The use of optimization methods and polytopes suggests that the paper could also belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) categories. Finally, the paper's focus on performance guarantees and numerical simulations suggests that it could also belong to the cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) category.
